Package: rollama
Type: Package
Title: Classify Text with LLMs on Ollama and Other Backends
Version: 0.4.0
Author: Luigi Palumbo <paluigi@users.noreply.github.com>
Maintainer: Luigi Palumbo <paluigi@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: A wrapper around the Ollama REST API and other inference engines
    (vLLM, SGLang, llama.cpp) for text classification with constrained output
    and confidence scoring. Provides adaptive constrained generation with
    divergence-aware confidence scoring and multi-call completion scoring
    with geometric-mean normalization. Supports multiple inference backends.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
